show.description: Simran, a resilient single mother, raises her triplets in secrecy after a traumatic night with business tycoon Aarav, unaware he’s the father. As fate brings them back together, past betrayals, Nayra’s jealousy, and hidden truths ignite a storm that tests love, loyalty, and identity.
